[{"id":"VR803943","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a uniform magnetic field and a charged particle traveling through the field on a circular path of radius r sub 1.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR803943.g02.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A charged particle entering a magnetic field follows a circular path of radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r sub 1\"><math alttext=\"r sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> within that field, as shown in the figure. A second charged particle, identical to the first, enters the same magnetic field traveling at a velocity twice that of the first and follows a circular path of radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r sub 2\"><math alttext=\"r sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>. What is the ratio of the second radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r sub 2\"><math alttext=\"r sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> to the first radius, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r sub 2, to, r sub 1\"><math alttext=\"r sub 2, to, r sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR803943_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 to 4\"><math alttext=\"1 to 4\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 to 2\"><math alttext=\"1 to 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 to 1\"><math alttext=\"2 to 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 to 1\"><math alttext=\"4 to 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]